announcement_github_body:
## Install gnostr 0.0.99

### Install prebuilt binaries via shell script

```sh
curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -LsSf https://github.com/gnostr-org/gnostr/releases/download/v0.0.99/gnostr-installer.sh | sh
```

### Install prebuilt binaries via powershell script

```sh
powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -c "irm https://github.com/gnostr-org/gnostr/releases/download/v0.0.99/gnostr-installer.ps1 | iex"
```

### Install prebuilt binaries via Homebrew

```sh
brew install gnostr-org/gnostr-org/gnostr
```
